      "raw_text": "(Scripps News Association.)\n\n\nHELENA. Mont, Nov. Sit Is\nannounced that the Great Northern\nwill start work within the next IL\nmonths on their proposed line\nwhich is to run from Somers, near\nkalispell, to a point near Jocko, on\nthe Northern Pacific, within the\nFlathead reservation. The delivery\nof the stuff to start work with is\nexpected within the next 80 days."
